Uses of Package
org.transitime.ipc.servers

  • Packages that use org.transitime.ipc.servers 
    Package Description
    org.transitime.ipc.servers
    Contains the classes for the servers, such as the core prediction system, that provide data via RMI.
  • Classes in org.transitime.ipc.servers used by org.transitime.ipc.servers 
    Class and Description
    CommandsServer 
    ConfigServer
    Implements ConfigInterface to serve up configuration information to RMI clients.
    PredictionsServer
    Implements the PredictionsInterface interface on the server side such that a PredictionsInterfaceFactory can make RMI calls in order to obtain prediction information.
    ServerStatusServer
    Runs on the server side and receives IPC calls and returns results.
    VehiclesServer
    Implements the VehiclesInterface interface on the server side such that a VehiclessClient can make RMI calls in order to obtain vehicle information.
